A note on the licence choice. CC-BY-4.0 is the right licence for this
material because it is educational text rather than software code. It
permits free reuse — quote it, translate it, teach with it, adapt it for
your team's internal documentation — with the single requirement that
attribution travels with it. This matches the spirit of the primer:
ideas free, artefacts where the value exchange happens.
